'''Aḍad''' d aḥric seg ufus n wemdan neɣ n kra n yiɣersiwen, yezga-d ɣer yixef n ufus. Afus n wemdan ɣur-s semmus (5) n yiḍudan, ttuseqdacen deg waṭas n tigawin am usami, tuṭfa, tira, atg.

==Tamawalt==
Asget : Iḍudan
Addad amaruz = Uḍad

==Iḍudan n ufus n wemdan==
Amdan ɣur-s semmus (5) n yiḍudan deg yal afus : 
* Adebbuz
* Uskin : Yezga-d gar udebbuz d uḍad ameqran
* Aḍad ameqran : D netta i d ameqran akk gar yiḍudan
* Warisem : Yezga-d gar uḍad ameqran d umeẓyan
* Aḍad ameẓyan : D netta i d ameẓyan akk gar yiḍudan
